thread.title: Darin

author: Darin
title: Darin
text: I bought a used file cabinet with missing keys. While web searching for a replacement lock/key set, I discovered EasyKeys.com. I had no idea I could order replacement keys. I was able to determine the exact keys I needed without talking to customer service. Yes, just by navigating the website. My keys arrived within the time frame Quote: d (within 5 days). The keys work perfectly. Now I have a commercial grade locking file cabinet with full functionality. I couldn't be more pleased with how easy and inexpensive it was. Thank you EasyKeys.com.
